                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Filtering",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The results are filtered based on the billing period range specified by the input parameters. Only records where the "
